snippet.textDisplay:
We used to have trend of kicking off with sufi music. Missed that. 
Also, an intro music video showing all singers is also missing. Rovalio did a great job in "Shuru karein!" Would've been great to witness that.

Coke Studio has so much history that an ordinary song can excite you. That's what just happened here. One extremely good thing was recognition of underground singers that I greatly admire.

Good Luck with upcoming songs! 👍
